<PERSON> Niels </PERSON> <PERSON> L. </PERSON> <PERSON> Hoyvald </PERSON> also was convicted. He received the same sentence as <PERSON> Lavery </PERSON> but was not involved in the appeal acted on today. <ORGANIZATION> Beech-Nut </ORGANIZATION> was fined $ 2 million after pleading guilty to selling adulterated and misbranded apple juice. The case is <PERSON> Lavery </PERSON> vs. <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION>, 89-216.
